\fs24 \cf6 Agent Skills allow you to extend Gemini CLI with specialized expertise, procedural workflows, and task-specific resources. Based on the\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://agentskills.io/"}}{\fldrslt \cf8 \strokec8 Agent Skills}}\'a0open standard, a \'93skill\'94 is a self-contained directory that packages instructions and assets into a discoverable capability.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs70 \cf11 \strokec11 Overview\cf6 \strokec6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf6 Unlike general context files ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://geminicli.com/docs/cli/gemini-md"}}{\fldrslt 
\f4\fs26 \cf8 \cb13 \strokec8 GEMINI.md}}), which provide persistent workspace-wide background, Skills represent\'a0
\f3\b on-demand expertise
\f0\b0 . This allows Gemini to maintain a vast library of specialized capabilities\'97such as security auditing, cloud deployments, or codebase migrations\'97without cluttering the model\'92s immediate context window.\
Gemini autonomously decides when to employ a skill based on your request and the skill\'92s description. When a relevant skill is identified, the model \'93pulls in\'94 the full instructions and resources required to complete the task using the\'a0
\f4\fs26 \cb13 activate_skill
\f0\fs24 \cb1 \'a0tool.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs70 \cf11 \strokec11 Key Benefits\cf6 \strokec6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\b\fs24 \cf6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Shared Expertise:
\f0\b0 \'a0Package complex workflows (like a specific team\'92s PR review process) into a folder that anyone can use.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Repeatable Workflows:
\f0\b0 \'a0Ensure complex multi-step tasks are performed consistently by providing a procedural framework.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Resource Bundling:
\f0\b0 \'a0Include scripts, templates, or example data alongside instructions so the agent has everything it needs.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Progressive Disclosure:
\f0\b0 \'a0Only skill metadata (name and description) is loaded initially. Detailed instructions and resources are only disclosed when the model explicitly activates the skill, saving context tokens.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs70 \cf11 \strokec11 Skill Discovery Tiers\cf6 \strokec6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf6 Gemini CLI discovers skills from three primary locations:\
