\f0\fs70 \cf11 \cb1 \strokec11 How it Works\cf6 \strokec6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b\fs24 \cf6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Discovery
\f0\b0 : At the start of a session, Gemini CLI scans the discovery tiers and injects the name and description of all enabled skills into the system prompt.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Activation
\f0\b0 : When Gemini identifies a task matching a skill\'92s description, it calls the\'a0
\f4\fs26 \cb13 activate_skill
\f0\fs24 \cb1 \'a0tool.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Consent
\f0\b0 : You will see a confirmation prompt in the UI detailing the skill\'92s name, purpose, and the directory path it will gain access to.\
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Injection
\f0\b0 : Upon your approval:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 The\'a0
\f4\fs26 \cb13 SKILL.md
\f0\fs24 \cb1 \'a0body and folder structure is added to the conversation history.\
\ls6\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 The skill\'92s directory is added to the agent\'92s allowed file paths, granting it permission to read any bundled assets.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f3\b \cf6 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	5	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec6 Execution
\f0\b0 : The model proceeds with the specialized expertise active. It is instructed to prioritize the skill\'92s procedural guidance within reason.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs58 \cf11 \strokec11 Skill activation\cf6 \strokec6 \
